Lady Iris Mountbatten https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lady_Iris_Mountbatten 0 Lady Iris Mountbatten (13 January 1920 – 1 September 1982) was an English actress and model, and a member of the Battenberg/Mountbatten family. She was a great-granddaughter and the youngest great-grandchild of Queen Victoria.
